item.title: Angewomon Cosplay - Digimon [self]
item.description:
Hi Imgur fam!! Last weekend I debuted my Angewomon [Digimon] cosplay at CCXP in Brazil! Angewomon was always my favorite Digimon character growing up, and I'm not sure how a cat evolves into an angel baddie, but hey, I'll take it ! Find more: IG: @MJasmine.Design
I'm beyond excited to share with y'all the results of months of work !
Mandatory photo with the sign
And yes, I had to take a photo with the Pennywise balloon !
So many folks had Angewomon tattoos, it was so cool to fangirl with them lol
With Blep, he was the real star of the show
I did a couple of interviews in Spanish and Portuguese. I also realized that not a lot people speak English in Brazil lol
Blep!
And the dressing rooms were insanely cool!!! I have never seen something like it in the US, and I've been to a lot of conventions lol
Enjoying my light up mirror moment
Egg head mode! Thanks for joining me on this adventure Imgur fam ! Find more on IG: @mjasmine.design
Cat tax! This is Socks, my escape artist cat ?
